---
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout>
	<Header />

	<!-- =====|| Main Section Start ||====== -->
	<main class="page">
		<div class="page__wrapper page__wrapper--alt">
			<!-- ==|| Terms & Conditions Hero Section Start ||== -->
			<div class="section-padding pt-120 pb-80">
				<div class="container">
					<h2
						class="site__heading-two-lg text-primary-grad-1 text-center"
						data-aos="fade-up"
						data-aos-duration="1000"
						data-aos-once="true"
					>
						Terms and Conditions
					</h2>

					<div
						class="mt-md-40 mt-20"
						data-aos="fade-up"
						data-aos-duration="1000"
					>
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold mt-20">
							Important Legal Notice
						</h6>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							By purchasing from PeptideLab, you acknowledge that all products are for research purposes only and agree to comply with all terms outlined below. These terms constitute a legally binding agreement.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold"
							>1. Acceptance of Terms</h6
						>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							By accessing or using PeptideLab's website and purchasing our products, you agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions. If you do not agree with any part of these terms, you must not use our website or purchase our products.
						</p>

						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							These terms constitute a legally binding agreement between you and PeptideLab. We reserve the right to modify these terms at any time, and such modifications shall be effective immediately upon posting on our website.
						</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold">2. Research Use Only</h6>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							ALL PRODUCTS ARE SOLD STRICTLY FOR LABORATORY AND RESEARCH PURPOSES ONLY.
						</p>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							Our peptides and research chemicals are NOT intended for:
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc">
							<li> Human consumption or self-administration </li>
							<li> Therapeutic, diagnostic, or medical use </li>
							<li> Administration to animals (in-vivo applications) </li>
							<li> Use as food additives or dietary supplements </li>
							<li> Any application outside legitimate scientific research </li>
						</ul>

						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">By purchasing, you acknowledge and warrant that you will use products exclusively for qualified research purposes in appropriate laboratory settings.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold"
							>3. Age Verification & Eligibility</h6
						>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							You must be at least 18 years of age to purchase from PeptideLab. By placing an order, you represent and warrant that:
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li> You are 18 years of age or older </li>
							<li>  You have the legal capacity to enter into this agreement </li>
							<li> You are not prohibited by law from purchasing these products </li>
							<li>  All information you provide is accurate and complete </li>
						</ul>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">We reserve the right to refuse service or cancel orders if we suspect misrepresentation of age or eligibility.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold"
							>4. Product Information & Accuracy</h6
						>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							We strive to provide accurate product information, including descriptions, specifications, purity levels, and pricing. However:
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li> Product images are for illustration purposes and may not reflect exact appearance </li>
							<li> Specifications are based on manufacturer data and third-party testing </li>
							<li> We reserve the right to correct errors in product information or pricing </li>
							<li> Certificates of Analysis (COAs) are provided when available and reflect batch-specific testing </li>
							<li>Product availability is subject to change without notice </li>
						</ul>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">If a product is listed at an incorrect price due to error, we reserve the right to cancel the order and refund your payment.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold"
							>5. Orders & Payment</h6>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							Order Acceptance: All orders are subject to acceptance by PeptideLab. We reserve the right to refuse or cancel any order for any reason, including but not limited to:
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li>Product availability</li>
							<li>Errors in pricing or product information</li>
							<li>Suspected fraudulent activity</li>
							<li> Failure to meet eligibility requirements </li>
						</ul>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">Payment: We accept major credit cards and other payment methods as displayed at checkout. Payment is due at the time of order placement. All prices are in USD.</p>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">Order Confirmation: You will receive an email confirmation once your order is placed. This does not constitute acceptance of your order—acceptance occurs when we ship your products.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold"
							>6. Shipping & Delivery</h6
						>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							Shipping Terms:
						</p>

						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li>We ship to addresses within the United States only</li>
							<li>Shipping costs are calculated at checkout based on weight and destination</li>
							<li>Estimated delivery times are provided but not guaranteed</li>
							<li>Products are shipped in discreet, unmarked packaging</li>
							<li>Cold chain integrity is maintained for temperature-sensitive products</li>
						</ul>

						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							Delivery: Once a package is shipped, risk of loss transfers to you. We are not responsible for:
						</p>

						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li>Delays caused by shipping carriers</li>
							<li>Failed delivery attempts due to incorrect addresses</li>
							<li>Packages lost or stolen after delivery confirmation</li>
							<li>Damage during shipping (claims must be filed with carrier)</li>
						</ul>
						<p>Tracking information will be provided once your order ships.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold"
							>7. Returns, Refunds & Exchanges</h6
						>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							Due to the nature of research chemicals and safety considerations:
						</p>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							Non-Returnable Products: All sales are final for opened, used, or reconstituted products. 
						</p>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							Eligible Returns: Unopened, unused products in original packaging may be returned within 14 days of delivery, subject to a 20% restocking fee.
						</p>
						<p>Damaged or Defective Products: If you receive damaged or defective products:</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li>Contact us within 48 hours of delivery with photographic evidence</li>
							<li>We will replace the product or issue a full refund at our discretion</li>
							<li>Return shipping costs for defective products will be covered by us</li>
						</ul>
						<p>Refund Processing: Approved refunds will be processed within 7-10 business days to your original payment method.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold"
							>8. Quality & Testing</h6
						>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							We are committed to providing research-grade peptides of the highest quality:
						</p>

						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li>All products are sourced from reputable manufacturers</li>
							<li>Batch-specific third-party testing is conducted when available</li>
							<li>Certificates of Analysis (COAs) are provided for verification</li>
							<li>Purity specifications are guaranteed within stated ranges</li>
						</ul>

						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">However, we make no warranties regarding:</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li>Suitability for any specific research application</li>
							<li>Results or outcomes from product use</li>
							<li>Performance in any particular protocol or study</li>
						</ul>
						<p>You assume all responsibility for proper handling, storage, and use of products.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold">9. Limitation of Liability</h6>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							TO THE MAXIMUM EXTENT PERMITTED BY LAW:
						</p>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">Products are provided "AS-IS" for research purposes only. PeptideLab shall not be liable for:</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li>Any direct, indirect, incidental, consequential, or punitive damages</li>
							<li>Injuries, adverse reactions, or health consequences from product misuse</li>
							<li>Loss of profits, data, or business opportunities</li>
							<li>Any claims arising from improper use or handling</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">Our total liability shall not exceed the purchase price of the product(s) in question.</p>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">You agree to indemnify and hold harmless PeptideLab, its officers, directors, employees, and agents from any claims, damages, or expenses arising from your use of our products.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold">
							10. Intellectual Property
						</h6>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							All content on this website, including text, graphics, logos, images, and software, is the property of PeptideLab or its licensors and is protected by copyright and trademark laws.
						</p>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">You may not:</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li>Reproduce, distribute, or display any content without written permission</li>
							<li>Use our trademarks or trade names without authorization</li>
							<li>Reverse engineer or create derivative works from our website or content</li>
						</ul>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold">
							11. Privacy & Data Protection
						</h6>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							We collect and process personal information in accordance with our Privacy Policy. By using our website and services, you consent to:
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li> Collection of personal and payment information</li>
							<li> Use of cookies and tracking technologies </li>
							<li>Storage and processing of your data as described in our Privacy Policy</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties except as necessary to process orders and comply with legal obligations.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold"
							>12. Legal Compliance</h6
						>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							You are solely responsible for ensuring your purchase and use of products complies with all applicable:
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li>Federal, state, and local laws</li>
							<li>Institutional regulations and policies</li>
							<li>Professional ethical standards</li>
						</ul>

						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							You warrant that you will not:
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li>Use products for unlawful purposes</li>
							<li>Violate any regulations governing research chemicals</li>
							<li>Resell products without proper licensing</li>
							<li>Export products in violation of export control laws</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">PeptideLab reserves the right to report suspected illegal activity to appropriate authorities.</p>
					</div>

					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold">13. Termination</h6>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							We reserve the right to:
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20">
							<li>Refuse service to anyone at any time</li>
							<li>Terminate or suspend your access to our website</li>
							<li>Cancel orders or refuse future orders</li>
						</ul>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							Reasons for termination may include:
						</p>
						<ul class="list-disc mt-20"	>
							<li>Violation of these Terms and Conditions</li>
							<li> Fraudulent or suspicious activity</li>
							<li>Misuse of products</li>
							<li>Providing false information</li>
						</ul> 
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							Upon termination, you must immediately cease using our products and website.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold">14. Dispute Resolution & Governing Law</h6>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							These Terms and Conditions shall be governed by and construed in accordance with the laws of the United States and the state in which PeptideLab is registered, without regard to conflict of law principles.
						</p>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							Arbitration: Any dispute arising from these terms or your use of our products shall be resolved through binding arbitration in accordance with the American Arbitration Association rules.
						</p>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							You waive any right to participate in class action lawsuits or class-wide arbitration.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold">15. Severability</h6>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							If any provision of these Terms and Conditions is found to be invalid or unenforceable, that provision shall be limited or eliminated to the minimum extent necessary, and the remaining provisions shall remain in full force and effect.
						</p>
					</div>
					<div class="mt-md-40 mt-20">
						<h6 class="fs-md-24 fs-18 text-black fw-bold">16. Contact Information</h6>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							For questions about these Terms and Conditions, please contact us through our website's contact form.
						</p>
						<p class="fs-md-18 fs-16 fw-400 mt-20">
							By completing a purchase, you acknowledge that you have read, understood, and agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions.
						</p>
					</div>
			</div>
			<!-- ==|| Terms & Conditions Hero Section End ||== -->
		</div>
	</main>
	<!-- =====|| Main Section Start ||====== -->

	<Footer />
</Layout>
